title: (x) www.yell.co.nz - Clicker {Yves}
content:
Hey,   
I am trying to find the name of a typeface.   
   
An example of the face can be found at [yell.co.nz](http://web.archive.org/web/20051109093942/http:/www.yell.co.nz/)   
   
The typeface I am looking is the one titling the site - " [www.yell.co.nz](http://web.archive.org/web/20051109093942/http:/www.yell.co.nz/)"   
   
Any clues would be grand.   
   
Cheers.
author: qwerty
